body.raw:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: Penalties
  description: Manages penalty (MT537) messages
  contact:
    name: Clearing & Settlement CIF
    email: clearing.settlement.front@seb.se
  license:
    name: SEB
    url: https://sebgroup.com/site-assistance/legal-notice
  version: 1.0.0
  x-seb:
    domain: DOM16
    tribe: TRI88
    art: ART98
    team: TEAM32
  x-seb-api:
    id: c504cd7c-e8d3-4514-8e0d-7c60ee0b9273
  x-seb-portal:
    category: savings
    state: active
    summary: Manages penalty (MT537) messages
servers:
  - url: https://penalties-api-gateway-custody.sebshift.dev.sebank.se
    x-environment: dev
  - url: https://penalties-api-gateway-custody.sebshift.stg.sebank.se
    x-environment: stage
  - url: https://penalties-api-gateway-custody.sebshift.prd.sebank.se
    x-environment: prod
paths:
  /log:
    get:
      tags:
        - Log
      parameters:
        - name: OrderBy
          in: query
          schema:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/LogOrderBy'
        - name: DateFrom
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            format: date-time
        - name: DateTo
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
            format: date-time
        - name: OrderDesc
          in: query
          schema:
            type: boolean
        - name: Take
          in: query
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
        - name: Skip
          in: query
          schema:
            type: integer
            format: int32
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
  /penalties-import:
    post:
      tags:
        - PenaltiesImport
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
          text/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
  '/re-import/{originalPenaltyImportId}/{approvedUserSid}':
    post:
      tags:
        - PenaltiesImport
      parameters:
        - name: originalPenaltyImportId
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
            format: uuid
        - name: approvedUserSid
          in: path
          required: true
          schema:
            type: string
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json-patch+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
          text/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
          application/*+json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/GeneralInformation'
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
  /re-enrich:
    patch:
      tags:
        - PenaltiesImport
      parameters:
        - name: ids
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: array
            items:
              type: string
              format: uuid
      responses:
        '200':
          description: Success
          content:
            text/plain:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: string
                  format: uuid
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: string
                  format: uuid
            text/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: string
                  format: uuid
components:
  schemas:
    ActiveStatusReason:
      enum:
        - NEWP
        - OTHR
        - RALO
        - SWIC
        - UPDT
      type: string
    CalculationDetail:
      required:
        - penaltyDate
      type: object
      properties:
        penaltyDate:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        missingReferenceDataFlag:
          type: boolean
        penaltyDiscountRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        securitiesSideAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        securitiesSideAmountCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        cashSideAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        cashSideAmountCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        financialInstrumentAttribute:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/FinancialInstrumentAttribute'
      additionalProperties: false
    CalculationMethodIndicator:
      enum:
        - SECU
        - MIXE
        - CASH
        - BOTH
      type: string
    Classification:
      enum:
        - SHRS
        - SOVR
        - DEBT
        - SECU
        - EFTS
        - UCIT
        - MMKT
        - EMAL
        - OTHR
        - ETFS
      type: string
    ContinuationIndicator:
      enum:
        - LAST
        - MORE
        - ONLY
      type: string
    CorporateActionEventIndicator:
      enum:
        - ACCU
        - ACTV
        - ATTI
        - BIDS
        - BMET
        - BONU
        - BPUT
        - BRUP
        - CAPD
        - CAPG
        - CAPI
        - CERT
        - CHAN
        - CLSA
        - CMET
        - CONS
        - CONV
        - COOP
        - CREV
        - DECR
        - DETI
        - DFLT
        - DLST
        - DRAW
        - DRCA
        - DRIP
        - DSCL
        - DTCH
        - DVCA
        - DVOP
        - DVSC
        - DVSE
        - EXOF
        - EXRI
        - EXTM
        - EXWA
        - INCR
        - INFO
        - INTR
        - LIQU
        - MCAL
        - MEET
        - MRGR
        - NOOF
        - ODLT
        - OMET
        - OTHR
        - PARI
        - PCAL
        - PDEF
        - PINK
        - PLAC
        - PPMT
        - PRED
        - PRIO
        - REDM
        - REDO
        - REMK
        - RHDI
        - RHTS
        - SHPR
        - SMAL
        - SOFF
        - SPLF
        - SPLR
        - SUSP
        - TEND
        - TNDP
        - TREC
        - WRTH
        - WTRC
        - XMET
      type: string
    FinancialInstrumentAttribute:
      required:
        - financialInstrumentIdentifier
      type: object
      properties:
        financialInstrumentIdentifier:
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        classification:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Classification'
        liquidFlag:
          type: boolean
          nullable: true
        smeGrowthMarketFlag:
          type: boolean
          nullable: true
        illiquidSharesRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        liquidSharesRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        corporateBondsRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        smeGrowthMarketRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        governmentMunicipalBondsRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        smeGrowthMarketBondsRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        otherInstrumentsRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        placeOfTrade:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        exchangeRateFromCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        exchangeRateToCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        exchangeRate:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
    Frequency:
      enum:
        - DAIL
        - MNTH
      type: string
    GeneralInformation:
      required:
        - activityFlag
        - continuationIndicator
        - functionOfMessage
        - pageNumber
        - safekeepingAccount
        - sendersMessageReference
        - statementDateTime
        - statementStructure
      type: object
      properties:
        pageNumber:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        continuationIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ContinuationIndicator'
        sendersMessageReference:
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        functionOfMessage:
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        preparationDate:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        statementDateTime:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        frequency:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Frequency'
        updateIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/UpdateIndicator'
        statementStructure:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/StatementStructure'
        safekeepingAccount:
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        activityFlag:
          type: boolean
        sendersBic:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        penalties:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Penalty'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
    LogOrderBy:
      enum:
        - Created
        - ErrorMessage
      type: string
    PartyCapacityIndicator:
      enum:
        - CSDP
        - CCPA
        - EXTE
        - ICSD
        - NAPI
        - NCSD
      type: string
    PaymentIndicator:
      enum:
        - APMT
        - FREE
      type: string
    Penalty:
      required:
        - penaltyListTypeIndicator
      type: object
      properties:
        statementPeriodFrom:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        statementPeriodTo:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        penaltyListTypeIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PenaltyListTypeIndicator'
        accountServiceProviderDepositary:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        penaltyCurrencies:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/PenaltyCurrency'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
    PenaltyCounterparty:
      type: object
      properties:
        counterpartyAccountServicerInfo:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        counterpartyRelatedPartyInfo:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        partyCapacityIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PartyCapacityIndicator'
        bilateralNetAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        bilateralNetAmountCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        penaltyDetails:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/PenaltyDetail'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
    PenaltyCurrency:
      required:
        - partyCapacityIndicator
        - sebRelatedPartyInfo
      type: object
      properties:
        currency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        penaltyDetectionDateTime:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        cashPenaltyPaymentReference:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        sebRelatedPartyInfo:
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        counterpartyAccountServiceProviderDepositary:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        partyCapacityIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PartyCapacityIndicator'
        globalNetAmountCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        globalNetAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        paymentDate:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        cashAccount:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        aggregatedDebitAmountCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        aggregatedDebitAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        aggregatedCreditAmountCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        aggregatedCreditAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        penaltyCounterparties:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/PenaltyCounterparty'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
    PenaltyDetail:
      required:
        - calculationMethodIndicator
        - computedAmount
        - computedAmountCurrency
        - numberOfDays
        - penaltyTypeIndicator
      type: object
      properties:
        penaltyCommonReference:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        penaltyReference:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        penaltyTypeIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PenaltyTypeIndicator'
        calculationMethodIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/CalculationMethodIndicator'
        amountAggregationFlag:
          type: boolean
          nullable: true
        penaltyStatus:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PenaltyStatus'
        activeStatusReason:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ActiveStatusReason'
        removeStatusReason:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/RemoveStatusReason'
        computedAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
        computedAmountCurrency:
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        numberOfDays:
          type: integer
          format: int32
        calculationDetails:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/CalculationDetail'
          nullable: true
        relatedTransaction:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/RelatedTransaction'
      additionalProperties: false
    PenaltyListTypeIndicator:
      enum:
        - FWIS
        - FWAM
        - CURR
      type: string
    PenaltyStatus:
      enum:
        - ACTV
        - REMO
        - NCOM
      type: string
    PenaltyTypeIndicator:
      enum:
        - SEFP
        - LMFP
      type: string
    Reason:
      required:
        - reasonCode
      type: object
      properties:
        reasonCode:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ReasonCode'
      additionalProperties: false
    ReasonCode:
      enum:
        - BENO
        - BLOC
        - BOTH
        - BYIY
        - CAIS
        - CANR
        - CDLR
        - CERT
        - CHAS
        - CLAC
        - CLAT
        - CLHT
        - CMON
        - COLL
        - CPEC
        - CSDH
        - CVAL
        - CYCL
        - DENO
        - DEPO
        - DISA
        - DKNY
        - DOCC
        - DOCY
        - FLIM
        - FROZ
        - GLOB
        - IAAD
        - INBC
        - INCA
        - LAAW
        - LACK
        - LALO
        - LATE
        - LINK
        - LIQU
        - MINO
        - MLAT
        - MONY
        - MUNO
        - NARR
        - NCON
        - NEWI
        - NOFX
        - OBJT
        - PART
        - PHCK
        - PHSE
        - PRCY
        - PREA
        - PRSY
        - REFS
        - REGT
        - SBLO
        - SDUT
        - SETS
        - STCD
        - YCOL
      type: string
    ReceiveDeliverIndicator:
      enum:
        - RECE
        - DELI
      type: string
    RelatedTransaction:
      required:
        - accountOwnerReference
      type: object
      properties:
        accountOwnerReference:
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        accountServicerReference:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        transactionIdentification:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        corporateActionReference:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        relatedInstructionReference:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        transactionDetail:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TransactionDetail'
      additionalProperties: false
    RemoveStatusReason:
      enum:
        - CORP
        - INSO
        - OTHR
        - RALO
        - SEMP
        - SESU
        - SUSP
        - SWIC
        - TEIM
      type: string
    StatementStructure:
      enum:
        - PENA
      type: string
    Status:
      required:
        - statusCode
      type: object
      properties:
        statusCode:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/StatusCode'
        reasons:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Reason'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
    StatusCode:
      enum:
        - PENF
        - PEND
      type: string
    TransactionDetail:
      required:
        - paymentIndicator
        - quantityAmount
        - receiveDeliverIndicator
        - settlementDateTime
        - transactionIndicator
      type: object
      properties:
        receiveDeliverIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ReceiveDeliverIndicator'
        paymentIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PaymentIndicator'
        settlementIndicator:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        transactionIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/TransactionIndicator'
        corporateActionEventIndicator:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/CorporateActionEventIndicator'
        acknowledgedStatusTimestamp:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        cutOffTimestamp:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        matchedStatusTimestamp:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        settlementDateTime:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        tradeDateTime:
          type: string
          format: date-time
          nullable: true
        safekeepingAccount:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        quantityAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
        postingAmount:
          type: number
          format: double
          nullable: true
        postingAmountCurrency:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        accountOwner:
          type: string
          nullable: true
        statuses:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/Status'
          nullable: true
      additionalProperties: false
    TransactionIndicator:
      enum:
        - SETT
        - CORP
      type: string
    UpdateIndicator:
      enum:
        - COMP
        - DELT
      type: string
